\* TRUE iff seq is prefixed with prefix.
HasPrefix(seq, prefix) ==
  /\ Len(seq) >= Len(prefix)
  /\ \A i \in 1..Len(prefix): seq[i] = prefix[i]

\* Remove prefix from seq.
TrimPrefix(seq, prefix) == [ i \in 1..(Len(seq)-Len(prefix)) |-> seq[i+Len(prefix)] ]

